"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?0/57/922/abstract/1\">",
"      Andersen HR, Falk E, Nielsen D. Right ventricular infarction: frequency, size and topography in coronary heart disease: a prospective study comprising 107 consecutive autopsies from a coronary care unit. J Am Coll Cardiol 1987; 10:1223.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?0/57/922/abstract/2\">",
"      Goldstein JA. Pathophysiology and management of right heart ischemia. J Am Coll Cardiol 2002; 40:841.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
